theorem dense_iff_closure_eq_univ {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
  Dense A ↔ closure A = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  -- The standard fact: A is dense iff closure A = univ
  have h : Dense A → closure A = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
    intro hA; simpa [Dense, Set.ext_...] using hA
  have h2 : closure A = (Set.univ : Set X) → Dense A := by
    intro hA; simpa using hA
  exact ⟨h, h2⟩
